h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent Currency Posting* link.
* Show List of *Agent Currency Posting* in [Landing Page|guide:ShowExhAgentCurrencyPostingActionService].

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "List Agent Currency Posting" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get list of *Agent Currency Posting* from server (default: 15 at Max).
* Following columns should show in grid view:
** Serial
** ID (Default: Invisible)
** Agent Name
** Amount
** Created By
** Created On
** Updated On

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** *Agent Currency Posting* will be listed in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

